From 0b321e9d65601ce3b61191019b1f5b8dc888b412 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Tue, 17 Feb 2026 18:50:20 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: migrate admin panel from REST API to Supabase direct
 queries

- Replace custom REST API backend with Supabase JS client
- Rewrite AuthContext to use Supabase Auth (signIn, signUp, signOut)
- Rewrite all API services to query Supabase directly
- Add profiles table support for user-store linking
- Update types to use UUID strings instead of numeric IDs
- Rename order_number -> public_id, customer_address -> delivery_address
- Update password reset flow for Supabase (no URL token param)
- Superadmin read/update/delete works; create requires Edge Function

https://claude.ai/code/session_01D3K1qWFLpRefHdHZNGjDQR
